imdb.plot outline: The Car Guy Show "Car Life & Car Culture" is about and for real "Car Guys." We check out their collections of interesting cars, walk through their incredible garages, attend their exciting events including car shows and car club gatherings and visit their favorite car museums, car auctions and more. We go where the car guys go and cover what the car guys want to see.
